  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I wound up again working-- once again working in the quarry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, on the three occasions that I was there, I-- I somehow wound up on the detail of the quarry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't remember doing any other work other than the quarry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Schindler, at that time, when he no longer could receive his workers from the concentration camp, he evidently began to scheme on how he could build a concentration camp for himself.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the best we could have-- we could determine at that time was that he did go off to Berlin and receive permission to build his own concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As, ?] in fact, building a concentration camp can be accomplished if he has a vital industry number 1.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, the vital industry was that the making of the pots and pans could be expanded into building some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cartridges for armaments, which is similar work as building pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lo and behold, the German authorities bought that, that this is such a vital industry that Schindler should be permitted to build his own concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he began to build a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He eventually got the people-- the 100 people plus some other people from Krakow-Plaszow to help him build this concentration camp adjoining the factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked on some of the barracks at the-- at the-- at the factory-- adjoining the factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schindler would mill around us at that time as-- as we were building this concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this concentration camp, to the best of my knowledge, it consisted of either five or six barracks, and it had watchtowers surrounding it, barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
